  <p>When you leave your computer, you can lock your screen to prevent other
  people from using it. You can also quickly switch users without logging out
  completely to give somebody else access to the computer, or you can
  suspend or power off the computer from the menu.</p>

  <list style="compact">
    <item>
      <p><link xref="shell-exit">ব্যৱহাৰকাৰী পৰিবৰ্তন কৰা, লগ আউট কৰা, আৰু আপোনাৰ কমপিউটাৰ বন্ধ কৰাৰ বিষয়ে অধিক জানক।</link></p>
    </item>
  </list>

